dc_title_s: Rand McNally official 1926 auto road map : Minnesota
dc_description_s: Copyright by Rand McNally & Company, Chicago, Ill.; On panel: "Compliments of Knoff-Peterson Hardware Co., Fergus, [sic] Falls, Minn."; Includes a continuation of the main map as an inset that shows the Lake Superior shoreline from Lutsen, Minn. to Port Arthur and Fort William, Ont.; Hardware dealers, fishing, camping, and tourist information, mileage table, and ill. on verso.|54 x 44 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:1,192,000|Minnesota Transportation Maps
